# Spotify Squad Health Check Overlay

When the user requests a Spotify Squad Health Check, use this framework as your scoring lens. Map each of the 11 original Spotify indicators to the 8 health dimensions, then score using Spotify's three-point scale.

---

## Spotify Scoring Scale

| Label | Meaning | Maps to RAG |
|-------|---------|-------------|
| Awesome 😊 | This is working great for us | 🟢 Green (4–5) |
| OK 😐 | There are some issues but we're managing | 🟡 Amber (2–3) |
| Needs Improvement 😞 | This is a real problem for us | 🔴 Red (1–2) |

Also capture **direction**: ↑ Getting Better / → Same / ↓ Getting Worse

Present scores using Spotify's original language (Awesome / OK / Needs Improvement) alongside the RAG equivalent so the output is useful for coaches who report in Spotify terms.

