## Output Format for Spotify Mode

In the Health Radar table, add a "Spotify Score" column showing the Spotify label alongside the standard score:

| Dimension | Status | Score | Spotify Score | Evidence | Trend |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Delivery | 🟡 Amber | 3/5 | OK 😐 | ... | ↓ |

At the top of the Coaching Brief, include a "Spotify Health Card" summary showing all 11 indicators with their Awesome / OK / Needs Improvement ratings — this is the format teams recognise from the original Health Check posters.

```
### Spotify Health Card
| Indicator        | Score              | Direction |
|------------------|--------------------|-----------|
| Easy to Release  | OK 😐              | ↓         |
| Suitable Process | OK 😐              | →         |
| Tech Quality     | Needs Improvement 😞 | ↓       |
| Value            | Needs Improvement 😞 | →       |
| Speed            | OK 😐              | ↓         |
| Mission          | OK 😐              | →         |
| Fun              | Awesome 😊         | →         |
| Learning         | OK 😐              | →         |
| Support          | Needs Improvement 😞 | ↓       |
| Pawns or Players | OK 😐              | →         |
| Teamwork         | Awesome 😊         | →         |
```
